{"tid":1530390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲：「你班死廢青想玩到幾時？」","createTime":"2019-09-02T02:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:09:25.000Z","uid":17812,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cc627d049890117744fcc1e9f7071e46d0f29ef7","tid":1530390,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:56:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">點解市民咁嬲？</span></strong><br />\n- 因為8月11 拉咗54 個人健健康康入去新屋嶺扣留中心，但有31 個人都骨折咁出返嚟。啲醫護人員話，佢哋得返層皮膚去連住啲肉。<br />\n- 因為仲有幾個女仔俾警察拉咗入去，傳聞仲俾警察輪姦。<br />\n- 因為仲有好多好多類似嘅事喺各區警署都有發生過，只係冇人俾人打完仲敢講出嚟、但仲有好多女仔勇敢指證要俾男警圍觀全裸搜身。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">點解要搞港鐵？</span></strong><br />\n- 因為7月21 號，港鐵放黑社會入元朗站打人！佢哋明明可以閂車門，隔開兩班人，但佢哋冇咁做，事後仲堅拒承認責任！<br />\n- 因為8月31號，警察衝入太子站打市民、喺室內放催淚彈。港鐵仲要幫警察拉閘，唔俾救護員入嚟搶救！最後仲要連埋警察成車駛走，而家全架車嘅人都未有消息，有鏡頭影到有兩個人俾警察打到無知覺，邊個知警察係咪打死咗無辜市民，想毀屍滅跡？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">點解要搞機場？</span></strong><br />\n- 就好似你哋話，當年中共批鬥你哋爸爸媽媽，批到癲咗。如果你當時聯同村入面其他人，一齊行出車站，想話俾其他村嘅人知道、如果當時有外國人，你又想俾佢哋知道中共幾咁恐怖；點知人哋話你影響民生，一樣道理。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">點解要影響「民生」？</span></strong><br />\n- 政府任意俾商家佬同大陸佬買貴晒啲樓就唔影響？後生仔連樓都買唔到呀！你哋成日話美國俾錢我哋搞亂香港，撇除係咪真係有俾錢，我當真係有；我想問，如果香港人人安居樂業，人哋要俾幾多錢，我哋先願意搞亂自己屋企？<br />\n- 知唔知而家小朋友講廣東話會俾同學仔杯葛，呢啲係你見唔到嘅民生呀。<br />\n- 仲有藥房呢、奶粉呢？你覺得呢啲係振興香港經濟？香港經濟唔係靠零售㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">你哋成日話，後生仔唔夠中共鬥㗎啦！</span></strong><br />\n- 後生仔冇樓冇物，一條爛命，鬥輸吧就。我未鬥過，點知唔得呀？<br />\n- 後生仔有讀歷史，知道極權統治一般唔會過70 年。後生仔知道，係機會啦！<br />\n- 後生仔而家有得上網、識其他語言、識得玩國際輿論，不如你都支持吓後生仔做一啲你當年做唔到嘅事？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">俾藍絲屋企人轟炸完，想發洩一吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩點半 添馬見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b5948fa5d1391954edfc3a680ce31f89306fc587","tid":1530390,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0218523e14baae0a2bb70fd4a3958378548d1b68","tid":1530390,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a85d3a86200d9406d10a027281ac8579f70918ce","tid":1530390,"uid":75759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb57d6a936824256223df3e2de0860aa914fd9c","tid":1530390,"uid":104672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"有排都未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a359a07d72fce614ade5d28475c0ad417da995f7","tid":1530390,"uid":31200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:06:22.000Z","msg":"無窮無盡唔會完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942da338fb0d90d9866013e5a6f453b95dec55a3","tid":1530390,"uid":126115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"點解唔問林奠想玩到幾時？ 都講到明五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"efe0a987d642417ed318e601f92c2f4b9ff2e726","tid":1530390,"uid":14605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:07:29.000Z","msg":"玩到香港獨立"},{"pid":"c2c50c5ec73c989dc7bdbfcd1a9f98beec7dcfe9","tid":1530390,"uid":300554,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bb57d6a936824256223df3e2de0860aa914fd9c","tid":1530390,"uid":104672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"有排都未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼 6條命 900被捕 無數斷手斷腳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831黨鐵恐襲傷者消息全無</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n九二九三大三罷！<br />\n設死線 升級持續罷工<br />\n日日罷工 日日入機場<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVP4X9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVP4X9g.jpg&h=c7d56cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5iA4Pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a16631db3ece17a33dd3ab8dad1c68cf29e69205","tid":1530390,"uid":276758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:08:12.000Z","msg":"下次直接答佢玩到你死果日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都要繼續玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a764cca510df339387c6578b849c1d4021307ac3","tid":1530390,"uid":174663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"死廢青表示你死我都未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔鐘意咪快啲兩腳一伸咪唔洗覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以個政府幾時收皮我咪考慮下停囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb82449016bf915318e752f7ec13857d7b6e6d0","tid":1530390,"uid":69688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"俾錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/face